text: Eotetrapodiformes is a clade of sarcopterygian fish including tetrapods and their ancestors.Two groups of stem tetrapods called tristichopterids and elpistostegalids. Eotetrapodiformes is part of the larger clade tetrapodomorpha. But it excludes the basalmost tetrapodomorphs, such as megalichthyiforms. ==Cladogram== Cladogram from Swartz, 2012: == References == Category:Lobe-finned fish
title: Eotetrapodiformes
